	abstract = {With the continuous improvement of artificial intelligence development level, enterprise architecture, as a systematic management framework, is increasingly valued by enterprises. Knowledge management and retrieval services in enterprise architecture are of great significance for improving operational efficiency and innovation capabilities of enterprises. To improve the accuracy and efficiency of enterprise architecture knowledge retrieval, research is conducted on designing enterprise architecture knowledge retrieval services based on RAG architecture, and using generative adversarial networks to increase adversarial training in the generation and retrieval process, thereby optimizing the coordination of retrieval and generation, and improving the accuracy and credibility of generated content. And based on it, use attention mechanism to improve and enhance retrieval accuracy. The outcomes denoted that the accuracy of the research method was as high as 91.42% and 92.06% in different datasets. The AUC reached 0.894 and 0.903 respectively. The shortest average response time and computation time for the research method are 2.51 seconds and 20.06 seconds, respectively. In datasets with larger data volumes, the longest average response time and computation time are also shorter than other algorithms, at 15.40s and 120.21s, respectively. In summary, the design of Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) enterprise architecture knowledge retrieval services based on improved generative adversarial networks has effectively improved the accuracy and efficiency of knowledge retrieval, providing support and reference for knowledge management of enterprise architecture.  © 2025 The Authors.},
